logic_summary: Reordered the chief complaint to describe tinnitus ('chirping sounds') first, as requested by the remarks and consistent with the case history where tinnitus preceded the realization of profound hearing loss.

patch_ops.value: I started hearing chirping sounds, like crickets, in my right ear. Later, I realized I couldn't hear anything from my right ear and developed severe dizziness.
